ion\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"name\";s:15:\"img_8441_01-min\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"inherit\";s:11:\"uploaded_to\";i:153;s:4:\"date\";s:19:\"2021-07-05 05:47:16\";s:8:\"modified\";s:19:\"2021-07-14 13:28:56\";s:10:\"menu_order\";i:0;s:9:\"mime_type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:4:\"type\";s:5:\"image\";s:7:\"subtype\";s:4:\"jpeg\";s:4:\"icon\";s:59:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-includes/images/media/default.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:2560;s:6:\"height\";i:1707;s:5:\"sizes\";O:8:\"stdClass\":18:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:78:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/IMG_8441_01-min-150x150.jpeg\";s:15:\"thumbnail-width\";i:150;s:16:\"thumbnail-height\";i:150;s:6:\"medium\";s:78:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/IMG_8441_01-min-300x200.jpeg\";s:12:\"medium-width\";i:300;s:13:\"medium-height\";i:200;s:12:\"medium_large\";s:78:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/IMG_8441_01-min-768x512.jpeg\";s:18:\"medium_large-width\";i:768;s:19:\"medium_large-height\";i:512;s:5:\"large\";s:79:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/IMG_8441_01-min-1024x683.jpeg\";s:11:\"large-width\";i:1024;s:12:\"large-height\";i:683;s:9:\"1536x1536\";s:80:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/IMG_8441_01-min-1536x1024.jpeg\";s:15:\"1536x1536-width\";i:1536;s:16:\"1536x1536-height\";i:1024;s:9:\"2048x2048\";s:80:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/IMG_8441_01-min-2048x1365.jpeg\";s:15:\"2048x2048-width\";i:2048;s:16:\"2048x2048-height\";i:1365;}}s:14:\"main_visual_sp\";s:77:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/IMG_8441_01-min-scaled.jpeg\";s:7:\"outline\";s:70:\"A chair for the futureofliving space where living and working overlap.\";s:16:\"clients_partners\";b:0;s:7:\"layouts\";a:11:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:50:\"l-text-2column:テキストのみ1カラム □■\";s:6:\"image1\";b:0;s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:98:\"We have designed a chair for the future of living space, where the place of life and work overlap.\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:50:\"l-text-2column:テキストのみ1カラム □■\";s:6:\"image1\";b:0;s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:479:\"As remote work has become the norm, there are more and more occasionsfor people to work at home, in their living place. The traditional idea of separating work and home is changing, and the home is becoming a new place where relaxation and workoverlap.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs a result, people need furnitures that have a function andappearance appropriate to the new environment, however it is not efficient to place differentfurniture for different purposesin a room of limited size.\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:42:\"l-image-3column:画像3カラム ■■■\";s:6:\"image1\";s:79:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/IMG_8441_01-min-1-scaled.jpeg\";s:6:\"image2\";s:77:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/IMG_8450_01-min-scaled.jpeg\";s:6:\"image3\";s:62:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2in1-min.png\";s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:50:\"l-text-2column:テキストのみ1カラム □■\";s:6:\"image1\";b:0;s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:518:\"The \"switch chair\" was created in light of these changes in society.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe \"switch chair\" is a minimalist chair designed for a space where work and home are combined, where one chair can be used for both living and working.The “desk chair style”, straightens the back and makesit easy to concentrate on work.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe “rockingchair style”, gently lowers the seat backward and creates a deeply relaxed posture. The chair can be switched to the suitable sitting style for each environment.\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:58:\"l-image1:画像のみ1カラム（通常サイズ）■□\";s:6:\"image1\";s:77:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/IMG_8511_03-min-scaled.jpeg\";s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:50:\"l-text-2column:テキストのみ1カラム □■\";s:6:\"image1\";b:0;s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:472:\"As the number of people working remotely increases, more people spend most of the day at their desks, and sitting in the same posture for long hours. Thishas become a major health problem, as it reduces blood flow in the muscles and leads to physical conditions such as back pain and stiff shoulders.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe switch chair allows you to sit for long periods of time without excessivelystrainingyour body byswitching the sitting positionfrom time to time.<br />\r\n\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:33:\"l-fullimage:画像ヨコイチ■\";s:6:\"image1\";s:71:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/chair_illustrator.png\";s:6:\"image2\";s:71:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/chair_illustrator.png\";s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:7;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:50:\"l-text-2column:テキストのみ1カラム □■\";s:6:\"image1\";b:0;s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:364:\"The frame is made of scratch-resistant bakedon coatingsteel pipes, and the seat is made fromdurable parachute cord. The simple and timeless form is designed to be used fora long time. In addition, the minimalist design makes it lightweight and allows for easy style changes by simply removing and rotating the leg frame, which is fixed to the seat with pipe clips.\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:8;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:42:\"l-image