e_q-300x188.jpg\";s:12:\"medium-width\";i:300;s:13:\"medium-height\";i:188;s:12:\"medium_large\";s:85:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Showfar_logo_negative_q-768x480.jpg\";s:18:\"medium_large-width\";i:768;s:19:\"medium_large-height\";i:480;s:5:\"large\";s:86:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Showfar_logo_negative_q-1024x640.jpg\";s:11:\"large-width\";i:1024;s:12:\"large-height\";i:640;s:9:\"1536x1536\";s:77:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Showfar_logo_negative_q.jpg\";s:15:\"1536x1536-width\";i:1280;s:16:\"1536x1536-height\";i:800;s:9:\"2048x2048\";s:77:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Showfar_logo_negative_q.jpg\";s:15:\"2048x2048-width\";i:1280;s:16:\"2048x2048-height\";i:800;}}s:14:\"main_visual_sp\";s:82:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Showfar_logo_negative-scaled.jpg\";s:7:\"outline\";s:100:\"Showfar®️ supports the business development of \"Private Mobility Agent Service\" by Persol Career.\";s:16:\"clients_partners\";b:1;s:7:\"layouts\";a:5:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:50:\"l-text-2column:テキストのみ1カラム □■\";s:6:\"image1\";b:0;s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:709:\"The \"Showfar®️\" demonstration project by Persol Career focuses on the time a person spends to commute to work which happens <regularly> <for a certain amount of time> <without exception>. Showfar®️ has designed a new experience that turns commuting time into a “time to meet new companies” by having users commute to work every week in a car driven by a dedicated driver on a fixed day of the week.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nquantum has worked on the business development of Showfar®️, which started its demonstration on Tuesday, December 22nd, 2020, in a wide range of areas including the PoC (Proof of Concept), MVP (Minimum Viable Product) development, and various design support simultaneously. <br />\r\n\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:50:\"l-text-2column:テキストのみ1カラム □■\";s:6:\"image1\";b:0;s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:451:\"quantum has worked on the business development of Showfar®️, which started its demonstration on Tuesday, December 22nd, 2020, in a wide range of areas including the PoC (Proof of Concept), MVP (Minimum Viable Product) development, and various design support simultaneously. <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.persol-career.co.jp/pressroom/news/service/2020/20201222_draft02/\" target=\"blank\">Click here for the press release from Persol Career</a>\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:58:\"l-image1:画像のみ1カラム（通常サイズ）■□\";s:6:\"image1\";s:64:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/showfar_1.jpeg\";s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:50:\"l-text-2column:テキストのみ1カラム □■\";s:6:\"image1\";b:0;s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:962:\"Showfar®️ is a service that allows users to have casual interviews with companies interested in their careers through a device that allows video calls while commuting in a car.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWith the spread of COVID-19, we live in an unpredictable time and there seems to be more and more occasions where we worry about our life, career and work styles. While individuals may not have the time to reflect on their careers or gather information before or after work hours or on holidays, Showfar®️ allows users to objectively and passively learn about their own value in the job market and understand the possibilities and demands for future career changes by simply riding to work.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFor companies, it provides an advantage in securing quality human resources, as it allows them approach those who are not familiar with the company or those who do not have the intentions to change careers immediately in a direct but less formal way.<br />\r\n\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:50:\"l-text-2column:テキストのみ1カラム □■\";s:6:\"image1\";b:0;s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:271:\"Showfar®️ special website: <a href=\"https://pre-experience.showfar.jp\" target=\"blank\">https://pre-experience.showfar.jp</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<small>Showfar\" is a patent pending by Persol Career.<br />\r\nShowfar\" is a registered trademark of Persol Career.<br />\r\n</small>\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}}s:14:\"use_mainvisual\";b:1;s:14:\"latest_journal\";s:0:\"\";}s:13:\"pll_sync_post\";a:0:{}}i:8;O:8:\"stdClass\":18:{s:2:\"id\";i:295;s:4:\"date\";s:19:\"2020-12-22T01:25:24\";s:8:\"date_gmt\";s:19:\"2020-12-21T16:25:24\";s:4:\"guid\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:52:\"http://localhost:10003/?post_type=project&#038;p=295\";}s:8:\"modified\";s:19:\"2021-07-12T16:39:08\";s:12:\"modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2021-07-12T07:39:08\";s:4:\"slug\";s:7:\"showfar\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"projects\";s:4:\"link\";s:40:\"http://localhost:10003/projects/showfar/\";s:5:\"title\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:12:\"Showfar®️\";}s:14:\"featured_media\";i:0;s:8:\"template\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"categories\";a:1:{i:0;i:25;}s:4:\"lang\";s:2:\"ja\";s:12:\"translations\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:2:\"en\";i:299;s:2:\"ja\";i:295;}s:3:\"acf\";O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:11:\"main_visual\";O:8:\"stdClass\":24:{s:2:\"ID\";i:297;s:2:\"id\";i:297;s:5:\"title\";s:21:\"Showfar_logo_negative\";s:8:\"filename\";s:27:\"Showfar_logo_negative_q.jpg\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:54777;s:3:\"url\";s:77:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Showfar_logo_negative_q.jpg\";s:4:\"link\";s:64:\"http://localhost:10003/projects/showfar/showfar_logo_negative-2/\";s:3:\"alt\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"author\";s:1:\"1\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\