る自動車で通勤してもらうことで、通勤時間を＜企業との出会いの時間＞へと変える新しい体験を設計したパーソルキャリアによる実証プロジェクト「Showfar®️（ショーファー）」。\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:50:\"l-text-2column:テキストのみ1カラム □■\";s:6:\"image1\";b:0;s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:448:\"2020年12月22日（火）より実証を開始した「Showfar®️」の事業開発に、quantumは実証実験（PoC）の実施、MVP（Minimum Viable Product）開発、各種デザイン支援など幅広い領域で並走し取り組んでいます。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.persol-career.co.jp/pressroom/news/service/2020/20201222_draft02/\" target=\"blank\">パーソルキャリアからのプレスリリースはこちら</a>\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:58:\"l-image1:画像のみ1カラム（通常サイズ）■□\";s:6:\"image1\";s:64:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/showfar_1.jpeg\";s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:50:\"l-text-2column:テキストのみ1カラム □■\";s:6:\"image1\";b:0;s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:988:\"「Showfar®️」は、車での移動中にビデオ通話が可能な端末を通して、利用者のキャリアに興味を持った企業とカジュアルな面談をすることができるサービスです。<br />\r\n <br />\r\n新型コロナウイルス感染症の拡大など予測不可能な時代において、人生やキャリア、働き方などについて悩む機会が増えている一方、就業時間前後や休日にキャリアについて省察したり、情報収集したりする時間がない個人でも、通勤時に乗車するだけで、客観的かつ受動的に自身の市場価値を知り、今後のキャリアチェンジの可能性や需要を把握することができます。<br />\r\n <br />\r\n企業にとっても、自社を知らない人材や、すぐに転職意向のない人材にもライトに、直接アプローチができるため、優秀な人材を確保しやすくなるなどのメリットがあります。\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:50:\"l-text-2column:テキストのみ1カラム □■\";s:6:\"image1\";b:0;s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:317:\"「Showfar®️」特設サイト：<a href=\"https://pre-experience.showfar.jp\" target=\"blank\">https://pre-experience.showfar.jp</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<small>「Showfar」はパーソルキャリアにて特許出願済みです。<br />\r\n「Showfar」はパーソルキャリアにて商標登録済みです。</small>\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}}s:14:\"use_mainvisual\";b:1;s:14:\"latest_journal\";s:0:\"\";}s:13:\"pll_sync_post\";a:0:{}}i:9;O:8:\"stdClass\":18:{s:2:\"id\";i:293;s:4:\"date\";s:19:\"2020-10-26T01:00:45\";s:8:\"date_gmt\";s:19:\"2020-10-25T16:00:45\";s:4:\"guid\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:52:\"http://localhost:10003/?post_type=project&#038;p=293\";}s:8:\"modified\";s:19:\"2021-07-12T16:40:28\";s:12:\"modified_gmt\";s:19:\"2021-07-12T07:40:28\";s:4:\"slug\";s:10:\"humofitr-2\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"publish\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"projects\";s:4:\"link\";s:46:\"http://localhost:10003/en/projects/humofitr-2/\";s:5:\"title\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:8:\"rendered\";s:12:\"HUMOFIT®️\";}s:14:\"featured_media\";i:0;s:8:\"template\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"categories\";a:1:{i:0;i:23;}s:4:\"lang\";s:2:\"en\";s:12:\"translations\";O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:2:\"en\";i:293;s:2:\"ja\";i:282;}s:3:\"acf\";O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:11:\"main_visual\";O:8:\"stdClass\":24:{s:2:\"ID\";i:283;s:2:\"id\";i:283;s:5:\"title\";s:33:\"20201023 HUMOFIT quantum web card\";s:8:\"filename\";s:37:\"20201023-HUMOFIT-quantum-web-card.png\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:1393082;s:3:\"url\";s:87:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/20201023-HUMOFIT-quantum-web-card.png\";s:4:\"link\";s:75:\"http://localhost:10003/projects/humofitr/20201023-humofit-quantum-web-card/\";s:3:\"alt\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"author\";s:1:\"1\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"name\";s:33:\"20201023-humofit-quantum-web-card\";s:6:\"status\";s:7:\"inherit\";s:11:\"uploaded_to\";i:282;s:4:\"date\";s:19:\"2021-07-06 14:04:21\";s:8:\"modified\";s:19:\"2021-07-06 15:14:20\";s:10:\"menu_order\";i:0;s:9:\"mime_type\";s:9:\"image/png\";s:4:\"type\";s:5:\"image\";s:7:\"subtype\";s:3:\"png\";s:4:\"icon\";s:59:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-includes/images/media/default.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:1280;s:6:\"height\";i:800;s:5:\"sizes\";O:8:\"stdClass\":18:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:95:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/20201023-HUMOFIT-quantum-web-card-150x150.png\";s:15:\"thumbnail-width\";i:150;s:16:\"thumbnail-height\";i:150;s:6:\"medium\";s:95:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/20201023-HUMOFIT-quantum-web-card-300x188.png\";s:12:\"medium-width\";i:300;s:13:\"medium-height\";i:188;s:12:\"medium_large\";s:95:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/20201023-HUMOFIT-quantum-web-card-768x480.png\";s:18:\"medium_large-width\";i:768;s:19:\"medium_large-height\";i:480;s:5:\"large\";s:96:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/20201023-HUMOFIT-quantum-web-card-1024x640.png\";s:11:\"large-width\";i:1024;s:12:\"large-height\";i:640;s:9:\"1536x1536\";s:87:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/20201023-HUMOFIT-quantum-web-card.png\";s:15:\"1536x1536-width\";i:1280;s:16:\"1536x1536-height\";i:800;s:9:\"2048x2048\";s:87:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/20201023-HUMOFIT-quantum-web-card.png\";s:15:\"2048x2048-width\";i:1280;s:16:\"2048x2048-height\";i:800;}}s:14:\"main_visual_sp\";s:63:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/HUMOFIT_1.png\";s:7:\"outline\";s:98:\"Total branding of a new material that senses body temperature and gently cares for people.<br />\r\n\";s:16:\"clients_partners\";b:1;s:7:\"layouts\";a:13:{i:0;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:50:\"l-text-2column:テキストのみ1カラム □■\";s:6:\"image1\";b:0;s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:337:\"quantum was in charge of the total branding of HUMOFIT®️, a new material developed by Mitsui Chemicals, Inc. that senses body temperature and gently cares for people.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe characteristics and appeal of the material are fully expressed through the naming, logo, website, video, and statement of the brand.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:50:\"l-text-2column:テキストのみ1カラム □■\";s:6:\"image1\";b:0;s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:203:\"<b>Name/Logo</b><br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe name \"HUMOFIT®️\" is a combination of the words \"HUman\", \"therMO\", and \"FIT\", as the new material senses human body temperature and gently wraps the body it touches.\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:58:\"l-image1:画像のみ1カラム（通常サイズ）■□\";s:6:\"image1\";s:63:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/logo-humo.png\";s:6:\"image2\";s:63:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/logo-humo.png\";s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:50:\"l-text-2column:テキストのみ1カラム □■\";s:6:\"image1\";b:0;s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:255:\"<b>Typeface</b><br />\r\n<br />\r\nHUMOFIT®️ has the characteristic of becoming soft when heated and hard when cooled. The HUMOFIT®️ logo typeface also reflects this dual material characteristic, expressing both hardness and softness in a single letter.\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:58:\"l-image1:画像のみ1カラム（通常サイズ）■□\";s:6:\"image1\";s:63:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/type_humo.png\";s:6:\"image2\";s:63:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/type_humo.png\";s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:50:\"l-text-2column:テキストのみ1カラム □■\";s:6:\"image1\";b:0;s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:306:\"<b>Brand Website</b><br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe white-based site was designed based on the concept of the color of the material itself and the innocent image of HUMOFIT®️ used in various products. By placing the brand movie at the top of the page, it naturally draws the visitors into the world of HUMOFIT®️.\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:39:\"l-image-2column:画像2カラム ■■\";s:6:\"image1\";s:74:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/humofit_webtop_short.png\";s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";s:74:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/humofit_webtop_short.png\";s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:7;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:50:\"l-text-2column:テキストのみ1カラム □■\";s:6:\"image1\";b:0;s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:368:\"<b>Brand Video</b><br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis video is designed to intuitively convey the temperature dependency and shape memory properties of HUMOFIT®️. We implemented the idea of “caring for people”, the origin of HUMOFIT®️.’s development, by expressing the appeal of the material that fits the body of all people, young and old, men and women.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:8;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:24:\"l-embed:YouTube等 embed\";s:6:\"image1\";b:0;s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:923:\"<b>Brand Statement</b><br />\r\nどれだけデジタルテクノロジーが発達しても、<br />\r\n人間が物に触れない日はありません。<br />\r\nやわらかい。かたい。さらさら。ざらざら。<br />\r\n私たちは毎日、いや、毎分、毎秒、「触感」とともに生きています。<br />\r\n物に触れた瞬間、心地よいと感じるときもあれば、<br />\r\n違和感や痛みを覚えるときもあります。<br />\r\n医療や介護、スポーツなど、さまざまな場面で、<br />\r\n日々無数に生まれるヒトとモノの間の“ミスマッチ”を解消することができたら。<br />\r\nヒトとモノの接点をもっとやさしくできたら。<br />\r\nそんな願いからHUMOFIT®️は生まれました。<br />\r\n私たちの開発の原点は、「ヒトに寄り添う」という発想です。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<b>Brand Items</b><br />\r\n\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";s:268:\"<iframe title=\"HUMOFOIT®の紹介動画\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WwD4dbwiTA4?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\";}i:9;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:50:\"l-text-2column:テキストのみ1カラム □■\";s:6:\"image1\";s:69:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/IMG_3228-scaled.jpg\";s:6:\"image2\";b:0;s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:933:\"<b>Brand Statement</b><br />\r\n<br />\r\nNo matter how advanced digital technology becomes.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere is never a day when we don\'t touch something.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSoft. Hard. Smooth. Coarse.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEvery day. No. Every minute, every second, we live with the sense of “touch.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere are times when we feel comfortable when we touch something.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere are other times when we feel discomfort or pain.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn a variety of situations, such as medical care, nursing care, and sports<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf we could solve the \"mismatch\" between people and products that occurs countless times every day.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhat if we could make the contact between people and products gentle?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHUMOFIT®️ was born from this wish.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe starting point of our development is the idea of \"caring for people\".<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<b>Brand Items</b><br />\r\n\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:10;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:33:\"l-fullimage:画像ヨコイチ■\";s:6:\"image1\";s:69:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/IMG_3228-scaled.jpg\";s:6:\"image2\";s:72:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/IMG_3225_05-scaled.jpg\";s:6:\"image3\";s:72:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/IMG_3192_01-scaled.jpg\";s:6:\"image4\";s:65:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/IMG_3185_03.jpg\";s:5:\"text1\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:11;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:49:\"l-image-4column:画像2カラム（2行・4つ）\";s:6:\"image1\";s:72:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/IMG_3238_09-scaled.jpg\";s:6:\"image2\";s:72:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/IMG_3225_05-scaled.jpg\";s:6:\"image3\";s:72:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/IMG_3192_01-scaled.jpg\";s:6:\"image4\";s:65:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/IMG_3185_03.jpg\";s:5:\"text1\";s:241:\"photography by ROBINHOOD photograph / Goichi Kondo<br />\r\n制作協力会社: 株式会社Rooftop<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHUMOFIT®️のウェブサイトは<a href=\"https://jp.mitsuichemicals.com/jp/special/humofit/\" target=\"blank\">こちら</a>。\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}i:12;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"layout_type\";s:50:\"l-text-2column:テキストのみ1カラム □■\";s:6:\"image1\";s:72:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/IMG_3192_01-scaled.jpg\";s:6:\"image2\";s:65:\"http://localhost:10003/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/IMG_3185_03.jpg\";s:6:\"image3\";b:0;s:6:\"image4\";b:0;s:5:\"text1\";s:224:\"photography by ROBINHOOD photograph / Goichi Kondo<br />\r\nProduction partner: Rooftop Inc.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nClick here for the<a href=\"https://jp.mitsuichemicals.com/jp/special/humofit/\" target=\"blank\">HUMOFIT®️website</a> \";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"embed\";N;}}s:14:\"use_mainvisual\";b:1;s:14:\"latest_journal\";s:0:\"\";}s:13:\"pll_sync_post\";a:0:{}}}s:7:\"headers\";a:10:{s:12:\"Content-Type\";s:31:\"application/json; charset=UTF-8\";s:16:\"X-WP-Cached-Call\";s:12:\"served-cache\";s:12:\"X-Robots-Tag\";s:7:\"noindex\";s:22:\"X-Content-Type-Options\";s:7:\"nosniff\";s:29:\"Access-Control-Expose-Headers\";s:27:\"X-WP-Total, X-WP-TotalPages\";s:28:\"Access-Control-Allow-Headers\";s:27:\"Authorization, Content-Type\";s:10:\"X-WP-Total\";i:43;s:15:\"X-WP-TotalPages\";i:5;s:4:\"Link\";s:66:\"<http://localhost:10003/wp-json/wp/v2/projects?page=2>; rel=\"next\"\";s:5:\"Allow\";s:3:\"GET\";}}','no');
