INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES (2061,256,'layouts_0_text1','quantum has assisted Lion Corporation\'s New Value Creation Program \"NOIL\" as a  supportive partner.\r\n\r\nThis project is based on the LIVE Plan (LION Value Evolution Plan), a mediumto longterm plan to realize Lion Corporation\'smanagement vision of becoming the\"Leading Company in the Future of Healthcare\" by 2030. The aim of this project is to discover issues, not just in the existing business fields of Lion Corporation, but issues relating to a wide range of healthcare fields,and create unprecedented solutions.\r\n\r\nUnder the theme of \"Businesses that Revolutionizes Conventional Healthcare,\" employees of LionCorporation and its domestic affiliates wereinvited to submit their business ideasthat solve the daily problems that users face. After multiple rounds of screening, business ideas that pass the final selection will be tested for commercialization and then launched. (Some services have already been launched.)\r\n\r\nThename of the project, NOIL, is thespelling of the company name, LION, written backwards, expressing the intention to break through barriers,to create new value.\r\n\r\nquantum supported this projectthrough program design, workshop management, and mentoring.');
